1
00:00:11,300 --> 00:00:12,700
♪If not for you♪

2
00:00:12,700 --> 00:00:15,960
♪I wouldn't have wanted
to make a name for myself♪

3
00:00:16,620 --> 00:00:17,940
♪Only when I have your love♪

4
00:00:17,940 --> 00:00:21,310
♪Is my invincibility not in vain♪

5
00:00:21,860 --> 00:00:23,330
♪The towering peaks I've conquered♪

6
00:00:23,330 --> 00:00:24,600
♪Leave me♪

7
00:00:24,600 --> 00:00:26,670
♪Feeling empty♪

8
00:00:26,670 --> 00:00:29,260
♪I've given everything♪

9
00:00:30,130 --> 00:00:31,210
♪Just to follow you♪

10
00:00:31,210 --> 00:00:33,900
♪Through life and death♪

11
00:00:34,690 --> 00:00:36,500
♪Could it be that love♪

12
00:00:36,500 --> 00:00:39,670
♪Is the true end of this life♪

13
00:00:39,880 --> 00:00:41,680
♪Why does every battle♪

14
00:00:41,680 --> 00:00:44,890
♪Bring deeper pain♪

15
00:00:45,290 --> 00:00:46,990
♪I never got it♪

16
00:00:46,990 --> 00:00:48,420
♪You once promised me♪

17
00:00:48,420 --> 00:00:50,240
♪You'd give me ordinary days♪

18
00:00:50,510 --> 00:00:51,620
♪Then I'd rather♪

19
00:00:52,020 --> 00:00:55,620
♪Face blades and fall♪

20
00:00:55,800 --> 00:01:01,010
♪Into your arms instead of the clouds♪

21
00:01:01,010 --> 00:01:04,210
♪I'll pass through layers of fog♪

22
00:01:04,210 --> 00:01:06,020
♪And barriers♪

23
00:01:06,300 --> 00:01:09,410
♪The world's rights and wrongs,
wins and losses♪

24
00:01:09,410 --> 00:01:11,600
♪Who's to weigh their worth♪

25
00:01:11,600 --> 00:01:13,060
♪Only love♪

26
00:01:13,060 --> 00:01:17,650
♪Gives me a sky as wide as the sea♪

27
00:01:19,380 --> 00:01:26,120
♪I only want to be your hero♪

28
00:01:27,240 --> 00:01:31,140
=The Prisoner of Beauty=

29
00:01:31,380 --> 00:01:34,180
=Episode 35=

30
00:01:34,260 --> 00:01:35,970
Out of fear that the truth
would come out,

31
00:01:36,050 --> 00:01:37,460
Liu Yan ordered a siege.

32
00:01:37,820 --> 00:01:39,290
We couldn't hold them off.

33
00:01:40,130 --> 00:01:42,260
General Wei Liang fought to
get me out of there,

34
00:01:42,900 --> 00:01:43,900
but he...

35
00:01:44,820 --> 00:01:45,660
He...

36
00:01:46,540 --> 00:01:47,380
I...

37
00:01:47,380 --> 00:01:48,320
It should've been me.

38
00:01:49,210 --> 00:01:50,130
Qiao Ci,

39
00:01:50,660 --> 00:01:51,500
look at me.

40
00:01:52,180 --> 00:01:53,690
Wei Liang went to fetch you, right?

41
00:01:54,540 --> 00:01:55,380
Where is he now?

42
00:01:56,290 --> 00:01:57,130
Look at me.

43
00:01:57,130 --> 00:01:57,980
Where is Wei Liang?

44
00:01:58,260 --> 00:01:59,170
He went to Yujun.

45
00:01:59,180 --> 00:02:00,260
Answer me. Where is he now?

46
00:02:01,260 --> 00:02:02,780
Look at me. Where is Wei Liang?

47
00:02:03,290 --> 00:02:04,570
Where is Wei Liang?

48
00:02:04,780 --> 00:02:05,660
Where is he?

49
00:02:05,660 --> 00:02:06,940
It should've been you.

50
00:02:06,940 --> 00:02:08,240
Why did it have to be him?

51
00:02:08,240 --> 00:02:09,380
Why not a Qiao?

52
00:02:09,380 --> 00:02:10,220
Wei Xiao!

53
00:02:10,410 --> 00:02:11,290
My Lord!

54
00:02:14,340 --> 00:02:15,180
Reporting!

55
00:02:15,890 --> 00:02:17,660
Liu Yan has taken Panyi with his troops.

56
00:02:22,850 --> 00:02:24,060
Pass down my orders:

57
00:02:27,100 --> 00:02:28,380
All troops, stay on alert.

58
00:02:29,130 --> 00:02:30,260
Tomorrow,

59
00:02:31,010 --> 00:02:32,170
we march on Panyi!

60
00:02:32,690 --> 00:02:33,530
Yes.

61
00:02:33,850 --> 00:02:34,690
My Lord.

62
00:02:35,380 --> 00:02:36,380
My Lord, My Lord.

63
00:02:36,690 --> 00:02:38,450
Let me lead a team to bring him back.

64
00:02:38,450 --> 00:02:40,130
I asked Wei Liang to go. He'll be fine.

65
00:02:40,130 --> 00:02:41,060
He just didn't see him.

66
00:02:41,060 --> 00:02:42,260
- Wei Qu.
- I'll get him back.

67
00:02:42,260 --> 00:02:43,290
Wei Qu, calm down!

68
00:02:43,290 --> 00:02:44,130
Wei Qu!

69
00:02:44,130 --> 00:02:46,170
Let me bring him back!

70
00:03:00,410 --> 00:03:01,250
Get up.

71
00:03:01,690 --> 00:03:02,530
Get up.

72
00:03:03,410 --> 00:03:05,220
My Lord, let me bring him back.

73
00:03:05,220 --> 00:03:06,060
Get up.

74
00:03:06,450 --> 00:03:07,410
Wei Liang will be okay.

75
00:03:07,690 --> 00:03:09,170
I'll go now. I'll bring him back!

76
00:03:09,170 --> 00:03:10,170
Wei Qu, hear my command.

77
00:03:12,100 --> 00:03:13,660
Tomorrow, take a cavalry unit

78
00:03:14,690 --> 00:03:15,530
to Kangjun.

79
00:03:16,850 --> 00:03:17,850
Find Qiao Ping.

80
00:03:19,940 --> 00:03:20,780
Bring

81
00:03:22,820 --> 00:03:23,660
Wei Liang back.

82
00:03:25,850 --> 00:03:26,850
I will bring him back.

83
00:03:29,340 --> 00:03:30,380
Yes, My Lord.

84
00:03:39,790 --> 00:03:41,420
- My Lady.
- Manman. Manman.

85
00:03:41,540 --> 00:03:43,260
- My Lady.
- Manman.

86
00:03:43,500 --> 00:03:44,940
- Manman.
- My Lady.

87
00:03:57,010 --> 00:03:57,850
Lie down.

88
00:04:13,220 --> 00:04:14,060
My Lord.

89
00:04:20,410 --> 00:04:21,610
Don't blame yourself.

90
00:04:26,220 --> 00:04:27,660
I just hate

91
00:04:30,850 --> 00:04:33,660
that I can't take this pain for you.

92
00:04:35,850 --> 00:04:38,340
You grew up with Wei Liang.

93
00:04:40,610 --> 00:04:42,850
You weren't real brothers,

94
00:04:44,220 --> 00:04:45,810
but he was like a real brother to you.

95
00:04:47,850 --> 00:04:50,370
Now, he was killed because of my family.

96
00:04:52,780 --> 00:04:54,370
Even if we paid with our lives,

97
00:04:55,410 --> 00:04:57,900
it wouldn't ease your pain.

98
00:05:04,220 --> 00:05:08,020
I once promised you
that I'd give you more kids

99
00:05:09,540 --> 00:05:10,930
and restore the past glory.

100
00:05:13,340 --> 00:05:15,900
But now I've made you lose Wei Liang.

101
00:05:20,900 --> 00:05:22,220
And Xiaotao...

102
00:05:29,250 --> 00:05:30,730
She's still...

103
00:05:31,140 --> 00:05:33,610
She's still waiting for Wei Liang.

104
00:05:41,250 --> 00:05:42,410
This isn't your fault.

105
00:05:49,980 --> 00:05:52,220
You've tried to balance both clans.

106
00:05:52,410 --> 00:05:53,410
It's been exhausting.

107
00:05:55,540 --> 00:05:56,610
Besides,

108
00:05:57,780 --> 00:05:59,170
Qiao Yue and Liu Yan

109
00:05:59,170 --> 00:06:00,250
did this.

110
00:06:03,290 --> 00:06:04,850
You had nothing to do with it.

111
00:06:09,020 --> 00:06:10,460
I will never blame you

112
00:06:11,170 --> 00:06:12,250
for this.

113
00:06:16,810 --> 00:06:17,660
But from now on,

114
00:06:19,050 --> 00:06:20,100
I may...

115
00:06:20,100 --> 00:06:20,980
I understand.

116
00:06:23,290 --> 00:06:25,730
Whether it's to avenge Wei Liang,

117
00:06:27,050 --> 00:06:29,460
take back Panyi for the people,

118
00:06:31,700 --> 00:06:34,340
seek justice for General Wei Liang,

119
00:06:37,340 --> 00:06:39,730
or punish my uncle's betrayal,

120
00:06:41,170 --> 00:06:43,250
you must go to war at once.

121
00:06:55,020 --> 00:06:56,100
Don't worry.

122
00:06:58,540 --> 00:06:59,580
I don't blame you.

123
00:07:08,370 --> 00:07:09,410
Thank you, Manman.

124
00:07:13,340 --> 00:07:14,490
You've never failed me,

125
00:07:15,460 --> 00:07:16,810
and I will never fail you.

126
00:07:19,100 --> 00:07:20,020
I promise.

127
00:07:21,370 --> 00:07:22,340
This matter

128
00:07:23,050 --> 00:07:24,410
will not implicate others.

129
00:07:25,460 --> 00:07:26,460
I give you my word.

130
00:07:33,140 --> 00:07:34,140
After I leave,

131
00:07:34,980 --> 00:07:36,290
take care of this family for me.

132
00:07:36,850 --> 00:07:38,020
Take care of yourself

133
00:07:45,020 --> 00:07:46,540
and Feifei.

134
00:07:53,100 --> 00:07:54,410
I may not be back

135
00:07:55,370 --> 00:07:57,170
in time for Feifei's birth.

136
00:08:03,730 --> 00:08:04,930
That's okay.

137
00:08:09,140 --> 00:08:10,220
This time,

138
00:08:13,220 --> 00:08:15,340
I won't see you off.

139
00:08:17,100 --> 00:08:19,460
Be careful on your journey.

140
00:08:22,250 --> 00:08:23,130
Don't worry.

141
00:08:26,180 --> 00:08:27,620
(Yujun)

142
00:08:30,580 --> 00:08:31,420
My Lord, don't worry.

143
00:08:31,420 --> 00:08:33,480
Wei Xiao and I will protect Yujun.

144
00:08:33,480 --> 00:08:34,530
We'll patrol day and night.

145
00:08:34,530 --> 00:08:35,730
Nothing will happen.

146
00:08:36,510 --> 00:08:38,460
Lady Xu and Lady Zhu
will take care of the Lady.

147
00:08:38,460 --> 00:08:39,730
You have nothing to worry about.

148
00:08:40,300 --> 00:08:41,140
Good.

149
00:08:46,730 --> 00:08:48,100
- Depart!
- Yes!

150
00:08:48,220 --> 00:08:49,060
Hyah!

151
00:09:24,100 --> 00:09:25,850
My Lady, take care of yourself.

152
00:09:25,850 --> 00:09:27,400
Don't strain yourself or harm the baby.

153
00:09:29,890 --> 00:09:31,300
How's Xiaotao?

154
00:09:32,730 --> 00:09:34,010
Xiaotao...

155
00:09:48,300 --> 00:09:50,100
You're really going to Yanzhou?

156
00:09:50,460 --> 00:09:52,820
I'll go and pick a real Yanzhou orchid

157
00:09:53,490 --> 00:09:54,490
to marry you.

158
00:10:01,100 --> 00:10:02,770
Are you asking me to serve you?

159
00:10:02,770 --> 00:10:03,610
No need for that.

160
00:10:04,060 --> 00:10:05,100
Just marry me.

161
00:10:05,580 --> 00:10:06,730
Once I've saved enough wages,

162
00:10:06,740 --> 00:10:07,660
I'll have the Lord ask

163
00:10:07,660 --> 00:10:09,260
for your mother's approval on my behalf.

164
00:10:09,420 --> 00:10:10,820
He values you.

165
00:10:11,220 --> 00:10:13,130
He's afraid he's not worthy of you,

166
00:10:13,490 --> 00:10:15,730
so he wants to do more.

167
00:10:16,010 --> 00:10:17,490
Only then will he feel at ease.

168
00:10:25,980 --> 00:10:26,820
You...

169
00:10:26,820 --> 00:10:27,980
Come back safe, okay?

170
00:10:27,980 --> 00:10:29,490
I've got your safety charm.

171
00:10:29,490 --> 00:10:30,400
Even if I get injured,

172
00:10:30,400 --> 00:10:32,460
I'll come back and ask
for your mother's approval.

173
00:10:32,460 --> 00:10:33,420
Pah, pah, pah.

174
00:10:33,420 --> 00:10:34,850
You won't get injured.

175
00:10:43,420 --> 00:10:44,820
Mine is a little gold dart.

176
00:10:45,340 --> 00:10:46,730
Every time we head to battle,

177
00:10:47,580 --> 00:10:49,730
we leave these little weapons behind.

178
00:10:49,730 --> 00:10:50,980
I want to give this to you.

179
00:10:51,300 --> 00:10:52,300
Seeing it

180
00:10:52,770 --> 00:10:54,300
will be like seeing me.

181
00:11:33,820 --> 00:11:35,020
Before General Wei Liang died,

182
00:11:35,850 --> 00:11:37,100
he asked me

183
00:11:38,530 --> 00:11:40,010
to bring this orchid to you.

184
00:11:40,890 --> 00:11:42,940
He must not have wanted you
to grieve like this.

185
00:11:45,370 --> 00:11:46,210
He said

186
00:11:49,460 --> 00:11:50,770
he'd bring the orchid

187
00:11:50,890 --> 00:11:52,980
and propose to me.

188
00:11:57,370 --> 00:11:58,530
Tell Xiaotao

189
00:11:58,530 --> 00:11:59,700
not to wait for me!

190
00:12:06,850 --> 00:12:08,490
This is from him.

191
00:12:10,340 --> 00:12:11,700
My mother said

192
00:12:12,650 --> 00:12:14,610
he was afraid I'd suffer

193
00:12:15,980 --> 00:12:18,180
and I'd look down on him one day

194
00:12:18,820 --> 00:12:21,530
so he made the betrothal gifts
so complex.

195
00:12:22,770 --> 00:12:24,420
She asked me to let him.

196
00:12:26,180 --> 00:12:27,650
She said it was more festive.

197
00:12:51,580 --> 00:12:54,220
(Panyi City, Yanzhou)

198
00:13:11,010 --> 00:13:11,850
Lord Yang.

199
00:13:12,700 --> 00:13:14,370
What's the situation in the city?

200
00:13:14,820 --> 00:13:15,860
The defenses are weak.

201
00:13:15,860 --> 00:13:17,100
We can't hold against Liangya.

202
00:13:17,100 --> 00:13:18,300
Panyi has completely fallen

203
00:13:18,300 --> 00:13:19,420
into Liu Yan's hands.

204
00:13:22,530 --> 00:13:23,400
Lord Yang,

205
00:13:23,410 --> 00:13:25,370
we once helped Lord Qiao
knock at the gate.

206
00:13:26,140 --> 00:13:27,010
So now...

207
00:13:27,010 --> 00:13:27,880
Should we have

208
00:13:27,890 --> 00:13:29,460
to turn to Liangya now?

209
00:13:34,650 --> 00:13:35,700
Listen.

210
00:13:36,980 --> 00:13:38,140
(Zhongzhou has defected)

211
00:13:38,160 --> 00:13:40,490
Lady Yulou has swayed Zhongzhou,

212
00:13:40,490 --> 00:13:42,530
dealing a major blow to Wei.

213
00:13:45,530 --> 00:13:47,980
Now, Wei Shao's allies
are turning to me.

214
00:13:48,700 --> 00:13:50,700
I wonder how he defies me now.

215
00:13:51,460 --> 00:13:54,730
But the Wei cavalry is still strong.

216
00:13:55,180 --> 00:13:57,730
Even without allies,
they're hard to defeat.

217
00:13:58,700 --> 00:14:00,470
Last time at Panyi,

218
00:14:00,480 --> 00:14:03,700
Liangya lost to them.

219
00:14:06,540 --> 00:14:07,850
Things are different now.

220
00:14:09,280 --> 00:14:10,770
Wei Shao must pass this way

221
00:14:10,990 --> 00:14:12,370
(Yongning City)
to reach us.

222
00:14:16,340 --> 00:14:17,530
Yongning City?

223
00:14:17,650 --> 00:14:19,650
He once built a dam here

224
00:14:19,650 --> 00:14:20,940
to divert floods.

225
00:14:21,050 --> 00:14:23,480
If the upper course breaks
and the lower course is blocked,

226
00:14:23,550 --> 00:14:25,060
what do you think will happen

227
00:14:25,060 --> 00:14:26,060
when he passes through?

228
00:14:26,610 --> 00:14:27,730
Brilliant.

229
00:14:29,130 --> 00:14:30,490
If it works,

230
00:14:30,850 --> 00:14:34,220
this place will become Wei Shao's grave.

231
00:14:35,980 --> 00:14:37,010
That day,

232
00:14:37,850 --> 00:14:40,490
Lady Qiao scared off my reinforcements.

233
00:14:41,250 --> 00:14:43,100
Today, I shall return that disgrace

234
00:14:43,650 --> 00:14:45,010
in full.

235
00:14:52,370 --> 00:14:53,210
Who's there?

236
00:14:53,850 --> 00:14:54,850
Come in.

237
00:14:58,300 --> 00:15:00,250
I'm here to deliver a report.

238
00:15:08,340 --> 00:15:10,220
The Wei army is on the move.

239
00:15:10,370 --> 00:15:11,610
My Lords,

240
00:15:11,610 --> 00:15:13,100
(Zhongzhou has defected)
what to do?

241
00:15:14,300 --> 00:15:15,220
Just as expected.

242
00:15:15,890 --> 00:15:17,490
Lord Yang, guard the Panyi dam.

243
00:15:17,890 --> 00:15:19,130
Be ready to release the water.

244
00:15:19,250 --> 00:15:22,100
Yes. I'll prepare to open the gate.

245
00:15:22,100 --> 00:15:23,180
Not to open it.

246
00:15:23,980 --> 00:15:25,100
Destroy it.

247
00:15:28,730 --> 00:15:30,010
Destroy the dam?

248
00:15:30,700 --> 00:15:31,890
That can't be.

249
00:15:31,980 --> 00:15:33,420
I've observed the clouds.

250
00:15:33,420 --> 00:15:34,890
Heavy rains are coming.

251
00:15:35,010 --> 00:15:37,650
If we break the dam now,

252
00:15:37,650 --> 00:15:39,770
the flood downstream
will be catastrophic.

253
00:15:39,980 --> 00:15:42,060
If the rain intensifies,

254
00:15:42,300 --> 00:15:44,180
the people will be doomed.

255
00:15:44,340 --> 00:15:45,730
The Lord of Wei...

256
00:15:45,730 --> 00:15:48,770
Wei Shao deserves it,
but the people along the way

257
00:15:49,180 --> 00:15:50,530
are innocent.

258
00:15:55,370 --> 00:15:57,730
To achieve greatness,
one can't fuss over trifles.

259
00:15:57,880 --> 00:15:59,420
Lord Yang, my late father trusted you.

260
00:15:59,420 --> 00:16:00,650
Surely you understand that.

261
00:16:00,650 --> 00:16:01,850
You call this a trifle?

262
00:16:17,370 --> 00:16:18,210
Fine.

263
00:16:20,060 --> 00:16:21,060
I understand.

264
00:16:21,530 --> 00:16:23,100
Governor, My Lord,

265
00:16:23,100 --> 00:16:25,180
I'll do as you command.

266
00:16:26,130 --> 00:16:29,180
But the dam of the Yongning Canal

267
00:16:29,180 --> 00:16:30,460
is made of giant stones.

268
00:16:30,460 --> 00:16:31,820
It's hard to destroy.

269
00:16:31,820 --> 00:16:34,180
If we use sulfur as an explosive,

270
00:16:34,180 --> 00:16:35,300
it must be placed

271
00:16:35,300 --> 00:16:37,100
beneath the load-bearing wooden beams.

272
00:16:39,180 --> 00:16:40,250
Without the right method,

273
00:16:40,530 --> 00:16:41,700
it won't work.

274
00:16:52,610 --> 00:16:53,610
My Lord,

275
00:16:54,140 --> 00:16:56,380
he makes a point.

276
00:17:06,700 --> 00:17:09,770
Then please wait here.

277
00:17:09,860 --> 00:17:11,980
I'll fetch the engineering diagram.

278
00:17:12,460 --> 00:17:15,140
With that, it'll be more effective.

279
00:17:15,630 --> 00:17:16,490
Very well.

280
00:17:16,490 --> 00:17:17,730
Be quick.

281
00:17:18,090 --> 00:17:18,930
Yes.

282
00:17:31,860 --> 00:17:34,330
The Yongning Canal project
is very complex,

283
00:17:34,700 --> 00:17:37,810
especially the section
from Panyi to Xindu.

284
00:17:37,810 --> 00:17:39,770
It took years to build.

285
00:17:39,940 --> 00:17:40,810
Now,

286
00:17:41,060 --> 00:17:42,810
