300
00:18:14,620 --> 00:18:16,140
I've seen

301
00:18:16,380 --> 00:18:18,730
that same ambition

302
00:18:19,460 --> 00:18:20,940
not only in Lord Qiao

303
00:18:20,940 --> 00:18:22,110
