315
00:18:55,010 --> 00:18:56,050
When this is over,

316
00:18:56,050 --> 00:18:57,220
you'll be rewarded.

317
00:18:58,570 --> 00:19:00,330
I'm just

318
00:19:00,570 --> 00:19:02,730
following orders.

319
00:19:02,730 --> 00:19:04,250
There's no hardship in that.

320
00:19:05,530 --> 00:19:07,010
But today,

321
00:19:10,140 --> 00:19:12,660
I'll have to fail Lord Qiao.

322
00:19:18,140 --> 00:19:20,620
Father built the canal for Yanzhou.

323
00:19:21,050 --> 00:19:22,490
Destroying it now

324
00:19:22,810 --> 00:19:26,420
