325
00:19:26,420 --> 00:19:28,290
You won't fail him.

326
00:19:28,900 --> 00:19:30,420
Hurry and unroll the diagram.

327
00:19:30,420 --> 00:19:31,620
Let's get started.

328
00:19:33,220 --> 00:19:34,060
Sure.

329
00:19:56,940 --> 00:19:58,380
