333
00:20:13,570 --> 00:20:15,770
I couldn't kill Liu Yan,

334
00:20:15,860 --> 00:20:17,570
but I can kill you!

335
00:20:17,570 --> 00:20:18,420
However,

336
00:20:18,570 --> 00:20:20,900
I'll have to fail Lord Qiao.

337
00:20:21,010 --> 00:20:22,730
Yang Feng, are you insane?

338
00:20:22,730 --> 00:20:24,770
How can you live after killing me?

339
00:20:25,420 --> 00:20:26,530
Without the dam

340
00:20:26,530 --> 00:20:27,900
and Panyi,

341
00:20:28,570 --> 00:20:29,730
what's the point

342
00:20:29,730 --> 00:20:31,380
