343
00:20:31,980 --> 00:20:33,090
Let him go.

344
00:20:33,570 --> 00:20:34,940
I'll spare your life.

345
00:20:34,940 --> 00:20:36,490
If Zhen Zhi could die for the cause,

346
00:20:36,770 --> 00:20:38,490
so can I.

347
00:20:39,900 --> 00:20:40,840
My Lord,

348
00:20:40,940 --> 00:20:41,980
