515
00:28:13,660 --> 00:28:15,620
with no mistakes.

516
00:28:19,180 --> 00:28:21,010
Grandmother, you are my family.

517
00:28:21,420 --> 00:28:22,900
Yujun is my home.

518
00:28:23,420 --> 00:28:25,140
I am the Lady of Wei.

519
00:28:25,810 --> 00:28:28,250
I will stand with the people of Yujun.

520
00:28:35,530 --> 00:28:36,730
I won't leave either.

521
00:28:37,660 --> 00:28:39,330
