522
00:28:39,980 --> 00:28:41,090
In my whole life,

523
00:28:41,900 --> 00:28:42,900
I've only wanted

524
00:28:42,900 --> 00:28:44,180
to make you happy,

525
00:28:45,420 --> 00:28:46,900
