526
00:28:47,050 --> 00:28:48,290
and often fail.

527
00:28:49,940 --> 00:28:51,380
If you can see me differently

528
00:28:51,980 --> 00:28:53,730
when I choose to stay,

529
00:28:54,220 --> 00:28:55,570
then I won't leave.

530
00:28:57,730 --> 00:28:58,570
Yes.

531
00:28:58,980 --> 00:28:59,860
Though I'm

532
00:29:00,080 --> 00:29:01,730
