533
00:29:02,980 --> 00:29:04,290
my sons

534
00:29:05,660 --> 00:29:07,010
and my husband

535
00:29:07,770 --> 00:29:09,530
would never be deserters.

536
00:29:12,810 --> 00:29:13,980
I will never

537
00:29:13,980 --> 00:29:15,250
shame them

538
00:29:15,250 --> 00:29:16,860
because of me.

539
00:29:17,010 --> 00:29:17,850
Mother,

540
00:29:19,090 --> 00:29:20,570
